OL,3,CForced adoption survivors will receive
OL,4,C'full apology on behalf of the state'
OL,6,FPhillipson told the Education
OL,7,FCommittee on Wednesday: "This
OL,8,Fgovernment will very soon be making a
OL,9,Ffull apology on behalf of the state to
OL,10,Fall of those affected by historic
OL,11,Fforced adoption in England.
OL,13,F"The prime minister will have more to
OL,14,Fsay on this shameful period in our
OL,15,Fhistory, reflecting the gravity of
OL,16,Fwhat has happened.
OL,18,F"But here and now, let me say to all
OL,19,Fof those affected, you will get the
OL,20,Fapology that you so profoundly
OL,21,Fdeserve."
